he is resting one hand on th board : 보드에 한손을 올려두고있다.
Among the four people the main is raising his hand : 네명중 손들고있는 남자
writing meterials : 필기구
there is a pen cup filled with several pens
she is resting her chin on her hand : 손위에 볼을 대다
she has a ponytail : 머리를 묶다.
he has his sleeves rolled up, : 소매를 올렸다
they are wearing T-shirts(주어에따라 복수/ 단수)
it looks like the one i have in my office
there are two people sitting face to face. 
Next to him
he is standing with his arams crossed
beard(비얼드) - 턱수염
there are plates of food
gathered together : 서로 모여있다.
everyone is wearing casual clothes : 캐주얼 옷을 입음
there are some tress and a grassy field : 나무와 잔디가 있다. 
